  "original_title": "\u0b85\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bc0\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b87\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf \u0b95\u0b9f\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bc6\u0bbe\u0bb4\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bbe\u0bb3\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0b8e\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0b95 \u0ba4\u0bc6\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0ba8\u0b9f\u0bb5\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8 \u0b8e\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc7\u0bbe\u0bae\u0bcd - \u0b85\u0bae\u0bc8\u0b9a\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b9f\u0b95\u0bcd\u0bb3\u0bb8\u0bcd \u0b89\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bbf",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "We will continue to take action against the trespassing Indian fishermen - Minister Douglas assured",
      "author": "Digital Desk 5",
      "body_lines": [
        "We will take action against the encroachments of Indian fishermen. Also, we have taken steps to provide the necessary fuel to the fishermen within this month's tight, said Douglas Devananda, Minister of Fisheries.",
        "He mentioned this in response to an interlocutory question asked by Dayasiri Jayasekara during oral question time in Parliament (04) on Monday.",
        "During his interlocutory question, Dayasiri Jayasekara said that due to the fuel problem, the marines could not go to sea to protect the sea border in the north.",
        "Therefore, Indian fishermen are encroaching on Sri Lankan waters and catching our fish.",
        "Today we cannot eat fish. Because only 12 boats out of 700 boats in Silapam have gone to sea.",
        "So what steps can be taken to stop the destruction being done by Indian fishermen in Sri Lankan waters? asked.",
        "A boat with 12 fishermen has been captured by the marines yesterday (the day before yesterday).",
        "Legal action will be taken against them if they continue to act in violation.",
        "Also, due to the countrywide fuel problem, fishermen are unable to go to the sea.",
        "I am personally involved in solving that problem. He said that we will take steps to provide the necessary fuel to the fishermen by the end of this month."
      ],
